text: Aya Sekine (born 12 April 1978) is a Japanese gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gunma Prefecture Category:Asian Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Gymnasts at the 1994 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for Japan Category:Medalists at the 1994 Asian Games
